---
title: Maple-Orange Glazed Duck Breast with Herby Potatoes and Walnut-Arugula Salad
description: A taste of Canadian bounty! Maple syrup, grainy mustard and rich duck breast make for a luxurious trio, while thyme-roasted potatoes meet their perfect match with rendered duck drippings.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/magret-de-canard-glace-a-lerable-et-a-lorange-dbf5923d.jpg
